.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md:382:- Doctor workflows that validate advisor health and rebuild state.
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md:389:Related skills:
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md:391:- `system-spec-kit` owns spec folders, memory, validation and packet governance.
