.opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md:12:Unified specialist providing: (1) Document quality pipeline with structure enforcement and content optimization, (2) OpenCode component creation (skills, agents, commands) with scaffolding, validation and packaging, (3) ASCII flowchart creation for visualizing workflows, (4) Install guide creation for setup documentation and (5) Feature catalog and manual testing playbook creation for inventory and validation packages.
