.opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md:184:- `assets/skill/` for skill creation templates, including `SKILL.md`, skill README, reference and asset scaffolds; `assets/agent_template.md` and `assets/command_template.md` at the assets/ root for agent and command creation templates.
