.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/manual_testing_playbook/08--scorer-fusion/001-five-lane-fusion.md:33:> **Structure deviation note (007-deferred-final).** This scenario uses a numbered-step plus Expected Signals plus Failure Modes shape instead of the canonical Prompt/Commands/Expected/Evidence/Pass-Fail/Failure-Triage subsections. The deviation is intentional for this skill playbook category to keep scenario semantics tightly bound to runtime output checks. See `references/decisions/deferred_decisions.md` §F34 for rationale.
