.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_query_cookbook.md:256:## 10. `hub_skills`
.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_query_cookbook.md:258:**Purpose**: Returns skills with the highest combined in plus out degree across all edge types.
