.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/graph/skill_graph_query_cookbook.md:342:**Worked example**: Use subgraph to build a visual neighborhood map around a skill before making changes. Radius 1 returns direct neighbors. Radius 2 includes neighbors of neighbors.
