.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/008-command-lane-asking/spec.md:2:title: "Feature Specification: Command lane-asking for the model-benchmark lane"
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/008-command-lane-asking/spec.md:3:description: "The model-benchmark lane of deep-agent-improvement has no command entry, and the existing command never asks which use-case lane the user wants. This phase makes the model-benchmark lane first-class at the command layer."
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/008-command-lane-asking/spec.md:6:  - "model-benchmark command entry"
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/008-command-lane-asking/spec.md:7:  - "start-model-benchmark-loop"
