.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/assets/agent-improvement/improvement_charter.md:8:Fixed policy template for a deep-agent-improvement run. Use it as the non-negotiable control layer that tells the mutator, scorer, reducer, and operator what kind of improvement workflow is allowed.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/assets/agent-improvement/improvement_charter.md:16:Defines the fixed policy boundary for a deep-agent-improvement run.
