.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/graph-metadata.json:196:    "causal_summary": "The 001 design names the mode-selector approach + three seams at the ADR level, but the build packet needs sharper implementation detail: exact interface contracts for each seam, how to generalize `dispatch-minimax.cjs` into a model-agnostic `dispatch-model.cjs`, how to port the 120/003 eval-rig scorer cleanly, and how to wire `mode` into `loop.cjs` without regressing the agent-improvement path. This also dogfoods MiniMax M2.7 as a deep-research executor.",
