.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/011-agent-lane-note/implementation-summary.md:53:The @deep-agent-improvement agent awareness note was upgraded from "Mode awareness" to "Lane awareness" across all 4 runtime mirrors, byte-identical. The new note frames the skill as two co-equal lanes (Lane A agent-improvement, Lane B model-benchmark) and states there is ONE agent so Lane B never spawns a second Claude agent.
