.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/017-two-lane-opus-deep-review/description.json:2:  "specFolder": "121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/017-two-lane-opus-deep-review",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/017-two-lane-opus-deep-review/description.json:12:    "121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode"
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:6:    "title": "Lane B YAML flags parse as booleans",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:7:    "file": ".opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/shared/loop-host.cjs",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:9:    "evidence": "parseArgs only captures --key=value; when a flag has no '=' it stores true at line 71 and ignores the following argv token. The Lane B YAML commands use space-separated flags like --profile {profile} and --outputs-dir {spec_folder}/improvement/benchmark-outputs.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:16:    "title": "Model benchmark never dispatches a model",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:17:    "file": ".opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/shared/loop-host.cjs",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:19:    "evidence": "The model-benchmark plan contains only materialize-benchmark-fixtures.cjs followed by run-benchmark.cjs; dispatch-model.cjs is never invoked before scoring existing {fixture.id}.md outputs.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:20:    "fix": "Insert a dispatch step that runs each fixture through dispatch-model.cjs with the selected executor/model and writes real model outputs before run-benchmark scores them; keep materialized fixture inputs separate from scored outputs."
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:26:    "title": "Lane B emits invalid session outcome",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:27:    "file": ".opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-model-benchmark-loop_auto.yaml",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:29:    "evidence": "The session_end command emits \"sessionOutcome\":\"benchmark-complete\", but SKILL.md freezes valid SESSION_OUTCOMES to keptBaseline, promoted, rolledBack, and advisoryOnly; the journal helper validates this enum.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:30:    "fix": "Use a valid outcome such as advisoryOnly for benchmark-only runs, or extend the journal enum and SKILL contract; apply the same fix to the confirm YAML."
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:37:    "file": ".opencode/commands/deep/start-model-benchmark-loop.md",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:39:    "evidence": "The command contract says executor/model are required when grader=llm, but the runtime command block passes only --profile, --outputs-dir, --scorer, and --grader.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:40:    "fix": "Thread --executor and --model through the YAML, loop-host, run-benchmark, and the grader/dispatcher path when grader=llm."
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:47:    "file": ".opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/shared/reduce-state.cjs",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:49:    "evidence": "stopOnDimensionPlateau only inspects bucket.dimensionScores; Lane B benchmark aggregate scores live in bucket.benchmarkRuns and are never checked, despite the Lane B YAML promising stop on 3+ identical aggregate scores.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:50:    "fix": "Add a benchmark aggregate plateau check over recent bucket.benchmarkRuns aggregateScore values and include a stop reason for benchmark plateau."
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:56:    "title": "Profile IDs fail before run-benchmark",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:57:    "file": ".opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/shared/loop-host.cjs",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:59:    "evidence": "loop-host forwards --profiles-dir only to run-benchmark, while the required first step materialize-benchmark-fixtures.cjs receives only --profile and --outputs-dir; a profile ID or custom profiles-dir cannot resolve before scoring starts.",
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/014-two-lane-deep-review/review/iterations/iteration-1.md:60:    "fix": "Forward --profiles-dir to the materializer and share the same profile path-or-id resolution logic used by run-benchmark."
