.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:59:This is **Phase 3** of packet 121 (add a model-benchmark mode to deep-agent-improvement). It executes the build-delta produced by phase 002's MiniMax M2.7 deep research (canonical source: `../002-implementation-deep-research/research/research.md`, §10 Build-delta). Phase 001 holds the architecture ADRs; this phase implements them.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:61:**Scope Boundary**: Implement the mode inside `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/` (+ a ported, decoupled scorer). Do NOT change the 120/003 rig (port source) or add new benchmark fixtures beyond what wiring needs.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:65:- 120/003 `eval-rig/` + `eval-loop/scripts/dispatch-minimax.cjs`, `score-variant.cjs`, grader `harness.cjs` (port source)
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:68:- `loop-host.cjs` (mode-switching entry point), `dispatch-model.cjs` (generic dispatcher), a decoupled scorer behind the scorer seam, mode-aware records + promotion, and the TST-1 identity test.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:80:deep-agent-improvement can improve agent definitions but cannot benchmark models/prompts; the 120/003 benchmark rig is packet-local and one-off. The 001 design + 002 research define how to add a `model-benchmark` mode, but the code does not exist yet.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:83:Ship a working `model-benchmark` mode alongside `agent-improvement`, sharing the three seams, with the existing agent-improvement path provably unchanged (byte-for-byte) when mode is unset.
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:94:- Ported, decoupled scorer behind the scorer seam (+ `buildGraderFn(mode)` factory)
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/003-build-benchmark-mode/spec.md:100:- New benchmark fixtures/profiles beyond wiring needs - separate concern
