.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/009-skill-md-two-lane/plan.md:51:This phase aligns SKILL.md with the two-lane reality the command layer already ships. The "Mode 4: Model-Benchmark" content currently nested inside the agent-improvement lane section is lifted into a co-equal Lane B section, the §1 lane cross-references are corrected to point at the real Lane B section, and the smart-router keeps its MODEL_BENCHMARK intent with a matching RESOURCE_MAP entry. All work stays inside SKILL.md, and no script, reference, asset, or runtime contract changes.
