.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-scripts-physical-reorg/spec.md:40:This phase moves the 16 deep-agent-improvement scripts plus the scorer subtree into agent-improvement, model-benchmark, and shared lane subdirs, making the two-lane split visible on disk for the last flat surface. It is the highest-risk phase because two path traps lie in wait: loop-host spawns children across all three lanes (TST-1 must stay byte-identical) and dispatch-model resolves config by walking up from `__dirname` (a wrong depth fails silently).
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/013-scripts-physical-reorg/spec.md:71:This is **Phase 13** of the deep-agent-improvement model-benchmark mode decomposition. It is the last and highest-risk phase.
