.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/002-implementation-deep-research/research/iterations/iteration-004.md:5:Implement the mode switch (agent-improvement | model-benchmark) wiring in `loop.cjs` (the orchestrating entry point) and ensure `materialize-benchmark-fixtures.cjs` is only invoked for model-benchmark mode. Research the actual code changes needed in reduce-state.cjs, converge.cjs, and the materialize plumbing.
