.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/007-benchmark-mode-hardening-review/review/iterations/iteration-011.md:52:   The grader path does not clamp/validate the model-returned numeric score before it feeds the weighted total, so a model can poison benchmark integrity. CONFIRM P1 on prior evidence; recommend a clamp `[0,1]` + parse-status gate. (Harness.cjs is in scope but I prioritized the headline + cwd defects within budget; this is carried forward, not re-disputed.)
