I have enough to write the iteration artifacts. The main design move is to make the report both machine-actionable (`report.json` with ranked bottlenecks) and operator-readable (`report.md` with evidence, caveats, replay), so Lane A or a follow-up packet can pick up exact fixes instead of prose hints.
